Title: Series: A Collection of Etchings after the Most Eminent Masters of the Dutch and Flemish Schools
Description: The Flight into Egypt; the Virgin and the Christ Child on donkey, led by Joseph; copy in reverse after Rembrandt. c.1782-1803 Etching
Curator's comments: For comment on the series see 1861,0413.56. For the original etching by Rembrandt and comment see F,4.100.
